linked protein gels in NMR studies of\nprotein dynamics and for modeling NMR relaxation in biological tissue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Dec 2013 17:20:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2014 10:04:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-13"}
