ed bubble. We compare this\nbubble with the observed ones and find excellent agreement, including similar\nfield strengths and velocity signals in the photosphere and chromosphere,\ntemperature deficits, ascent speeds, expansion velocities, and lifetimes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Dec 2013 20:48:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
